et-while-hiking-with-her-family-in-israel-180986359/</link><description>这位3岁的男孩捡起了一个古老的迦南圣甲虫，可追溯到中间青铜时代</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 16:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/toddler-discovers-3800-year-old-egyptian-amulet-while-hiking-with-her-family-in-israel-180986359/</guid></item><item><title>AI可以在150多年前在大火中被摧毁的Delacroix壁画复活吗？</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/can-ai-resurrect-a-delacroix-mural-that-was-destroyed-in-a-fire-more-than-150-years-ago-180986354/</link><description>一个名为Digital Delacroix的新项目正在培训法国画家风格的尖端技术，以揭示Lost Artwork的秘密</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 14:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/can-ai-resurrect-a-delacroix-mural-that-was-destroyed-in-a-fire-more-than-150-years-ago-180986354/</guid></item><item><title>每个人都在谈论的MLB“鱼雷”蝙蝠背后的科学 - 他们如何工作？他们真的更好吗？</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-science-behind-the-mlb-torpedo-bats-that-everyones-talking-about-how-do-they-work-and-are-they-really-better-180986356/</link><description>这些蝙蝠是由物理学家开发的，其最宽的部分称为枪管，靠近球员的手，以便在他们的“最佳位置”上击球更有机会击球</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:39:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-science-behind-the-mlb-torpedo-bats-that-everyones-talking-about-how-do-they-work-and-are-they-really-better-180986356/</guid></item><item><title>艺术展览使瑞士的罗纳冰川永生，预计到2050年就会消失</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/art-exhibition-immortalizes-switzerlands-rhone-glacier-predicted-to-disappear-by-2050-180986285/</link><description>Ohan Breiding的“冰川肚子”结合了实验电影和摄影，以反思失落的时刻，并与之抗争</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:28:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/art-exhibition-immortalizes-switzerlands-rhone-glacier-predicted-to-disappear-by-2050-180986285/</guid></item><item><title>增强的大脑植入物将中风幸存者的思想转化为使用人工智能的几乎即时演讲</title><link>https://w